message.body: Hey Faye! Just got your VM. Hope u had a fantastic bachelorette party haha
I'm out with a friend at the moment - can we catch up/discuss logistics tomorrow or Tues? Not sure what your availability is...

Hi!! Not a problem! Yes let's chat tomorrow or tues! Tomorrow I think I'll be free btwn 530 & 630, then after 8ish...and tues I should be free after 730ish. Or if those times don't work, I'm free all evening Wednesday! :-)
I'm on the metro with spotty service, can I call you in about 10?
So good to talk to you last night!!!!
Agreed!!! So glad we finally got back in touch! ! :-D
